text: The 2009 Malaysia Super Series, not to be confused with the 2009 Malaysia Open Grand Prix Gold, was a badminton tournament held from January 6 to January 11, 2009 in Putra Indoor Stadium, Malaysia. ==Winners== {| class="wikitable" style="font-size:90%" !Tour !Men's singles !Women's singles !Men's doubles !Women's doubles !Mixed doubles |- | Malaysia Super Series | Lee Chong Wei | Tine Rasmussen | Jung Jae-sung Lee Yong-dae | Lee Hyo-jung Lee Kyung-won | Nova Widianto Lilyana Natsir |} ==External links== *Offizielle Website *tournamentsoftware.com Category:Malaysia Open (badminton) Category:Sport in Kuala Lumpur Category:2009 in Malaysian sport Malaysia
